      ## Subscribing tags
      
      You can subscribe for tag by few ways:
      
      ### Your subscriptions page.
      
      Click on **Subscribe for more** link on the bottom of your sidebar
      
      ![Subscribe for more](http://img404.imageshack.us/img404/5179/screenshot20120612at206.png)
      
      ### Subscribe on tag's page
      
      ### Autosubscriptions
      
      After you submit posts or comments or wiki we subscribe for tags you are have written for.
      
      ![Subscribe posts](http://img205.imageshack.us/img205/4541/screenshot20120612at207.png)
      
