      ## Writing comments
      
      On the post's page you can comment it.
      
      ![New comment](http://img651.imageshack.us/img651/2097/screenshot20120612at218.png)
      
      ## Following users
      
      In order to expand your flow and will be more social you can navigate to user's page and follow him (her)
      
      ![Follow user](http://img27.imageshack.us/img27/8366/screenshot20120612at221.png)
      
      ## Observing posts
      
      After you submit new post or comment you will automatically observing that post.
      
      Also you can observe/unobserve it manually.
      
      ![Observe post](http://img825.imageshack.us/img825/4079/screenshot20120612at223.png)
      